What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this course to anyone who is familiar with basic conducting technique and wants to become more comfortable conducting more difficult works.

For an undergrad, this course makes a good 5th class. The average workload is lighter than other courses I've taken. I also learned a lot by watching the grad students; having them there was very helpful.
